channel.title: Silab V6.0? Can't get Skill Capes
channel.description: Hi. A while ago I got reports from my members that ::pick 10704 was turning out to be a key of some sort. Naturally I investigated this and found that SilabSoft had been updated. I copied her ItemDef into my Item.cfg but when I try to ::pick 14074 (attack skill cape), it doesn't do anything. It's only a problem with numbers higher than 11000 (the maximum id I had before V6). I tried making a command (silab1) that would give you most Skill Capes but when I tested this I got a 'fatal' error, disconnected and a load of rubbish about OutOfArrays or something on packetsend or something like that. Can someone please tell me what's wrong![br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 01, 2007, 03:26:29 PM[/size][hr]Also found another error. I can't seem to eat any type of food. Sorry but I really need help with this aswell. You can be Mod on my server if you fix this!
